{"tid":1091174,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"獨立報：紅魔斥1億鎊斟辛祖 重建曼聯皇朝","createTime":"2019-04-04T03:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T13:03:44.000Z","uid":54373,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3262acdf23ae1e9882ca752e0efb5c1a6ee28a7b","tid":1091174,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=bcca512a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯計劃夏天出手，斥資1億鎊斟介炙手可熱的超新星查頓辛祖。<br />\n<br />\n多蒙特超新星查頓辛祖（Jadon Sancho）備受球壇關注，有傳已進入曼聯的轉會雷達，為蘇斯克查重建王朝招兵買馬。英國《獨立報》披露，紅魔願意拿出1億鎊轉會費，再加球員作為籌碼，從拜仁慕尼黑、巴黎聖日耳門等勁旅手中，搶去19歲英格蘭國腳查頓辛祖。<br />\n<br />\n辛祖全面上位，目前已交出16個助攻，同時射入8球，除了球員之外，球隊正尋找體育總監回巢，負責買賣球員。<br />\n<br />\n這位翼鋒本為曼城青年軍，2017年被多蒙特挖走，目前已是英格蘭大國腳，擁有4頂喼帽，前途無可限量。"},{"pid":"d41eaf6bb5d11c4684d020f7a85030fe323a546e","tid":1091174,"uid":23734,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"買埋alex alan<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e09c2492c4227339c43863539d0eda40a0174c","tid":1091174,"uid":32861,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T03:17:50.000Z","msg":"皇騎做總監<br />\nAlex amy alan加盟教練團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a7cde5f1623670ab858ff0a42765b048bcd717","tid":1091174,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"買到返去會唔會變水貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d841d9794381bb9a27e019fa1377f522446e303c","tid":1091174,"uid":34572,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.t